00:18:48.000 --> 00:18:49.000
The E.E.S.S.

00:18:49.000 --> 00:18:50.000
And this is the second-guided school.

00:18:50.000 --> 00:18:51.000
This is all black school.

00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:52.000
All black school.

00:18:52.000 --> 00:18:53.000
And what did he say?

00:18:53.000 --> 00:18:56.000
He said that we should be put out of school.

00:18:56.000 --> 00:18:57.000
Simple as that.

00:18:57.000 --> 00:19:02.000
And he did not put us out of school, but he said that we should be put out of school.

00:19:02.000 --> 00:19:03.000
Why?

00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:11.000
Because apparently the superintendent had gotten on him because the letter came his office from us at his school.

00:19:11.000 --> 00:19:13.000
And he was responsible for us.

00:19:13.000 --> 00:19:18.000
