00:19:21.000 --> 00:19:28.000
You're standing up for what you know is right and you could call them to the principal's office and you're reprimanded.

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:32.000
At the time, I didn't feel it was fair.

00:19:32.000 --> 00:19:36.000
I thought that he should have been a part of what we were doing.

00:19:36.000 --> 00:19:42.000
But as I got older, I understood what he didn't do anymore in our favor.

00:19:42.000 --> 00:19:43.000
Why was that?

00:19:43.000 --> 00:19:50.000
Because when you have a family and obligations, you look at things a lot different when you don't have obligations.

00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:55.000
If that was happening now, at my age, I don't know if I would take the same stand, too.

00:19:55.000 --> 00:19:59.000
But I don't know if I would have been any different about the letter.

00:19:59.000 --> 00:20:04.000
