00:20:04.000 --> 00:20:06.000
But I understand his point now.

00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:08.000
I mean, I hold up the gist up for that.

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:14.000
So afterwards, you write the letter and you get called into the principal's office.

00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:18.000
