00:20:32.000 --> 00:20:34.000
We would have recess back in those days.

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:35.000
So who outside?

00:20:35.000 --> 00:20:37.000
They would keep the hours.

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:40.000
And actually, I was president of senior class.

00:20:40.000 --> 00:20:44.000
And they forced me to resign.

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:50.000
They didn't take it from me, but they put it to me in a way that I knew what they wanted me to do.

00:20:50.000 --> 00:20:54.000
And they were excited that it's brilliantly glenched behind that letter.

00:20:54.000 --> 00:20:57.000
