00:20:57.000 --> 00:21:01.000
Because clearly, people knew that you had written this letter.

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:04.000
Nobody questioned.

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:09.000
The students, the few that were involved, were involved, and the ones that were not.

00:21:09.000 --> 00:21:12.000
I mean, they didn't question what was going on with their new ideas.

00:21:12.000 --> 00:21:13.000
How did you do that?

00:21:13.000 --> 00:21:16.000
How can we get involved?

