No, they had not.

00:23:11.000 --> 00:23:12.000
And this is the county sheriff?

00:23:12.000 --> 00:23:14.000
Yes, from the county.

00:23:14.000 --> 00:23:20.000
He and his deputies, I guess, and other citizens or the white citizens.

00:23:20.000 --> 00:23:23.000
They were not dressed in white rolls and they got a sub of it.

