ZT Matthews is what we call him.

00:23:31.000 --> 00:23:32.000
He was the sheriff's name.

00:23:32.000 --> 00:23:35.000
Phil Sambri, and I wasn't afraid that night.

00:23:35.000 --> 00:23:37.000
I don't really know why, but I wasn't afraid that night.

00:23:37.000 --> 00:23:40.000
And I remember every year, I read from Rome at 8.

00:23:40.000 --> 00:23:41.000
That night.

00:23:41.000 --> 00:23:42.000
Charles Sambri.

