But I can remember sitting on the ground and you can see if anybody would burn a church there, do anything.

00:24:15.000 --> 00:24:21.000
And that was one of the statements I remember saying to myself, as I stood in the watch, the smoke.

00:24:21.000 --> 00:24:23.000
Do you remember your father's reaction?

00:24:23.000 --> 00:24:24.000
He was hurt.

00:24:25.000 --> 00:24:29.000
I don't remember any conversation, per se, but I know he was hurt about it.

