00:25:42.000 --> 00:25:47.000
but there was older folks who lived close to us who were not involved, and they didn't want to harm them.

00:25:47.000 --> 00:25:50.000
So that's the reason I heard that they didn't burn out house.

00:25:50.000 --> 00:25:58.000
And I remember my day at the making statement that one of the white women tried to run him off the road as he was going to all get into work one morning.

00:25:58.000 --> 00:26:02.000
So that was three of us, I guess I feel.

00:26:02.000 --> 00:26:11.000
