00:26:11.000 --> 00:26:14.000
Not of any grave nature.

00:26:14.000 --> 00:26:20.000
I mean, they were vigilant in watching.

00:26:20.000 --> 00:26:23.000
But other than that, I don't think of anything that we actually did.

00:26:23.000 --> 00:26:25.000
We didn't go out and buy guns or that kind of thing.

00:26:25.000 --> 00:26:26.000
And that's what you ask.

00:26:26.000 --> 00:26:28.000
And no, nothing I remember.

00:26:28.000 --> 00:26:30.000
On that level.

