And Dr. King, the speech, of course.

00:33:09.000 --> 00:33:12.000
And just a Jackson's, some other people that I reckon that's from.

00:33:12.000 --> 00:33:14.000
Coming in out doing a movie.

00:33:14.000 --> 00:33:17.000
John Lewis and John Lewis.

00:33:17.000 --> 00:33:20.000
But other than that, you know, I was pretty much alone.

00:33:20.000 --> 00:33:21.000
Just enjoying the day.

00:33:21.000 --> 00:33:22.000
For what it was worth.

00:33:22.000 --> 00:33:25.000
Had no idea the impact that we were making.

00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:31.000
Had I known how important that day was, I would have saved some of the buttons

00:33:31.000 --> 00:33:33.000
of those kind of things that were there.

00:33:33.000 --> 00:33:36.000
So I'll have any of that in one of the members of it.

00:33:36.000 --> 00:33:39.000
And so after, I, I, I, I afterward, all right.

00:33:39.000 --> 00:33:44.000
I mean, you the, the, the, the speeches are done on the mall.

00:33:44.000 --> 00:33:48.000
And it's just time to go, you just pack up and head on.

00:33:48.000 --> 00:33:51.000
We just go back to the train because we didn't take luggage.

00:33:51.000 --> 00:33:52.000
We go back to the train.

00:33:52.000 --> 00:33:55.000
You don't train coming home.

00:33:55.000 --> 00:33:57.000
Just to train right.

00:33:57.000 --> 00:33:58.000
That's about it.

00:33:58.000 --> 00:34:00.000
What do you think of Washington DC?

00:34:00.000 --> 00:34:03.000
This is much of it, except for the, you know, the part.

00:34:03.000 --> 00:34:05.000
Because there were so many people you could only see with,

00:34:05.000 --> 00:34:09.320
right in front of you actually and most of the time there was somebody that says back.

00:34:09.320 --> 00:34:13.560
So as far as the money and the money and so on, you really didn't get to see that in

00:34:13.560 --> 00:34:16.640
the sense of the word, not to actually enjoy it.

00:34:16.640 --> 00:34:18.160
You just knew that they were there.

00:34:18.160 --> 00:34:19.160
That's all.

00:34:19.160 --> 00:34:24.240
When people curious about your experience when you came back home, I really, nobody

00:34:24.240 --> 00:34:25.240
really asked.

00:34:25.240 --> 00:34:29.200
Does that really remember asking me, you know, how was it or what did you learn or got

00:34:29.200 --> 00:34:31.200
thing to what asked?

00:34:31.440 --> 00:34:34.600
Now, had you seen King before, down here?

00:34:37.440 --> 00:34:40.160
I remember him coming to my daughter doing the time to church at Burmese,

00:34:40.160 --> 00:34:41.560
standing on the ground there.

00:34:41.560 --> 00:34:45.960
That was the first, I think, the only time I could saw him in person like that.

00:34:45.960 --> 00:34:48.880
Well, that actually had that church at the Burmese.

00:34:52.120 --> 00:35:00.440
So watching the DC was on the first time you spent the night away from your mother's home,

00:35:00.440 --> 00:35:02.640
on the out from under your mother's roof.

00:35:02.640 --> 00:35:05.640
Second time you go up for the physical, please.

00:35:05.640 --> 00:35:07.640
Third time, you're not coming back, right?

00:35:07.640 --> 00:35:10.680
I mean, you're about to, you're in the army.

00:35:10.680 --> 00:35:12.680
What was basic training like?

00:35:12.680 --> 00:35:13.680
Basic training was fun, actually.

00:35:16.440 --> 00:35:19.640
I played basketball in high school, so I was still in shape.

00:35:19.640 --> 00:35:23.000
And, you know, I wasn't intimidated.

00:35:23.000 --> 00:35:25.160
Basic training was, it was rigorous but fun.

00:35:25.960 --> 00:35:30.760
I learned a lot out of two.

00:35:30.760 --> 00:35:35.360
I like to say I was timid a little bit before that.

00:35:35.360 --> 00:35:39.000
And it helped me to kind of redefine my personality.

00:35:39.000 --> 00:35:42.200
And it was a good thing for me, I think.

00:35:42.200 --> 00:35:48.280
Matter of fact, I believe that all young men on a health be able to spend those two years

00:35:48.280 --> 00:35:50.120
minus the war thing, of course.

00:35:50.120 --> 00:35:55.080
You know, but it's a good training ground for young men.

00:35:55.080 --> 00:35:59.000
It helped me get a footing as to be responsible for them,

00:35:59.000 --> 00:36:01.000
say, or the need to be in the work with a group of people,

00:36:01.000 --> 00:36:04.800
and take orders and be responsible for the people.

00:36:04.800 --> 00:36:09.080
Now, your unit wasn't mostly black, black and white mixed,

00:36:09.080 --> 00:36:14.920
mixed, Spanish, American, you know, Puerto Ricans.

