What'd you think?

00:36:23.400 --> 00:36:25.640
I mean, here you coming from rural?

00:36:25.640 --> 00:36:26.960
I never thought about it in a way.

00:36:26.960 --> 00:36:32.600
I mean, it wasn't like I had any special regard or special concerns.

00:36:32.600 --> 00:36:36.760
You know, you just, you do what you're supposed to do,

00:36:36.760 --> 00:36:40.160
and you demand to be respectful space.

00:36:40.160 --> 00:36:40.960
And that's pretty much it.

00:36:40.960 --> 00:36:42.360
And you respect that as well.

00:36:42.360 --> 00:36:44.520
So I didn't see that as a problem.

00:36:44.520 --> 00:36:48.600
Actually, it was a good experience.

00:36:48.600 --> 00:36:51.120
And where are you stationed?

00:36:51.120 --> 00:36:53.280
