So I ended up going to an all-more unit when I was out there.

00:37:10.800 --> 00:37:12.280
We went to Germany.

00:37:12.280 --> 00:37:14.640
So it was about all my communication training.

00:37:14.640 --> 00:37:18.680
And you sent over to West Germany.

00:37:18.680 --> 00:37:20.840
