00:37:20.840 --> 00:37:22.920
is in Kissing Germany.

00:37:22.920 --> 00:37:25.320
And that's where I spent the 20-day months

00:37:25.320 --> 00:37:28.560
of my service time there.

00:37:28.560 --> 00:37:31.160
So over two years, it gets around rough to an area.

00:37:31.160 --> 00:37:33.000
It gets rough.

00:37:33.000 --> 00:37:38.200
And so now, not only you're not in Toronto County,

00:37:38.200 --> 00:37:40.320
earlier, your mom was rude, but you're not

