00:39:50.440 --> 00:39:52.560
In the movement.

00:39:52.560 --> 00:39:57.840
So you do about 2.5 years or so.

00:39:57.840 --> 00:39:59.280
You come out.

00:39:59.280 --> 00:40:00.320
And you come back home.

00:40:00.320 --> 00:40:02.560
Yes.

00:40:02.560 --> 00:40:06.200
