00:40:06.200 --> 00:40:12.440
I remember being all about the likes and those kind of things.

00:40:12.440 --> 00:40:13.280
Wow.

00:40:13.280 --> 00:40:14.480
This is what I left.

00:40:15.480 --> 00:40:16.160
Got home.

