And that was the biggest shock.

00:40:33.360 --> 00:40:35.320
There's not a lot of economic that changed.

00:40:35.320 --> 00:40:36.360
I had changed.

00:40:36.360 --> 00:40:39.680
I would not do with some of the things I had

00:40:39.680 --> 00:40:41.200
had been doing before.

