I wanted more out of life.

00:40:43.320 --> 00:40:46.360
And that's what changed most, you know,

00:40:46.360 --> 00:40:47.840
surrounded that much.

00:40:47.840 --> 00:40:50.320
Well, except for my father built another house on the spot

