00:58:02.160 --> 00:58:04.560
So I don't have to question whether you like me.

00:58:04.560 --> 00:58:07.080
And I know you don't.

00:58:07.080 --> 00:58:11.040
So I don't have to expose myself to you.

00:58:11.040 --> 00:58:13.360
Well, he got mad at me.

00:58:13.360 --> 00:58:15.440
He didn't speak to me at all.

00:58:15.440 --> 00:58:19.480
But that's the difference I see between North and South.

00:58:19.480 --> 00:58:23.400
There's a perceived freedom.

00:58:23.400 --> 00:58:26.360
But it really is not there sometimes.

00:58:26.360 --> 00:58:27.920
It's perceived.

00:58:27.920 --> 00:58:29.520
But on the heath is really not.

00:58:29.520 --> 00:58:32.880
In a lot of ways, I like to South better

00:58:32.880 --> 00:58:34.960
because I don't have to question.

00:58:34.960 --> 00:58:36.000
I don't have to expose myself.

00:58:36.000 --> 00:58:38.640
I already know where I'm accepted there pretty much.

00:58:38.640 --> 00:58:41.160
And it's up to me whether or not I want to venture past

00:58:41.160 --> 00:58:42.440
that or not.

00:58:42.440 --> 00:58:44.440
But that, you kind of give that false security

00:58:44.440 --> 00:58:47.320
that you can do these things.

00:58:47.320 --> 00:58:50.440
And that's the difference I see between South and North.

00:58:50.520 --> 00:58:53.480
And there is more economic separation

00:58:53.480 --> 00:58:56.280
than it is white, black separation here.

00:58:59.160 --> 00:59:00.960
You just, it's just a difference in the race here.

00:59:00.960 --> 00:59:03.080
But there, if you don't have the money

00:59:03.080 --> 00:59:06.680
and the way they separate there, they just take the money,

00:59:06.680 --> 00:59:08.200
go to suburb with them.

00:59:08.200 --> 00:59:10.480
And it's happening here.

00:59:10.480 --> 00:59:13.800
We have, we asked about conditions.

00:59:13.800 --> 00:59:17.360
We have black mayors, but the economics are gone.

00:59:17.640 --> 00:59:19.440
The base for support and the city,

00:59:19.440 --> 00:59:21.440
they're gone to suburb attacks.

00:59:21.440 --> 00:59:22.160
Yeah.

00:59:22.160 --> 00:59:25.520
So you can't be aware of it, but if you don't have money.

00:59:25.520 --> 00:59:30.520
And then we'll accuse of not being good stewards.

00:59:32.600 --> 00:59:34.280
But how can you be in the city in a town?

00:59:34.280 --> 00:59:34.800
Yeah.

00:59:34.800 --> 00:59:35.720
How can you be a good student?

00:59:35.720 --> 00:59:37.160
You don't have a pause-up rate.

00:59:37.160 --> 00:59:39.120
The infrastructure is gone.

00:59:39.120 --> 00:59:41.080
You know, people complain about the stand-up.

00:59:41.080 --> 00:59:42.240
But there's nothing money there.

00:59:42.240 --> 00:59:43.880
I mean, the tax base is gone.

00:59:43.880 --> 00:59:45.640
So you can't read it very, very, very.

00:59:47.360 --> 00:59:51.040
Oh, it's a round.

00:59:51.040 --> 00:59:52.240
Thank you very much.

00:59:52.240 --> 00:59:53.720
This is no wonderful.

00:59:53.720 --> 00:59:54.720
Keep it right.

